properties.currency_code: The ISO 3 currency code. For example, `usd`.
properties.is_default: Whether the currency is the default in the store.
properties.store: The store this currency belongs to.

properties.name: The name of the store
properties.default_sales_channel_id: The ID of the store's default sales channel.
properties.default_region_id: The ID of the store's default region.
properties.default_location_id: The ID of the store's default stock location.
properties.metadata: Holds custom data in key-value pairs.
properties.supported_currencies:
The supported currencies in the store.

@expandable
properties.supported_locales:
The supported locales in the store.

@expandable

properties.id: The ID of the store locale.
properties.locale_code: The locale code in BCP 47 format. For example, `en-US`.
